00:03:52.746 --> 00:03:55.276 A:middle
What if my app reached
the limits?

00:03:55.816 --> 00:04:00.316 A:middle
How much will I have
to pay Apple?

WEBVTT
X-TIMESTAMP-MAP=MPEGTS:181083,LOCAL:00:00:00.000

00:03:55.816 --> 00:04:00.316 A:middle
How much will I have
to pay Apple?

00:04:00.526 --> 00:04:03.126 A:middle
Second question we got
