Okay? So now let's
take a look at a demo

00:08:40.405 --> 00:08:42.285 A:middle
of the CloudKit calculator.

00:08:42.385 --> 00:08:46.196 A:middle
This is on
developer.apple.com/cloudkit.

00:08:46.196 --> 00:08:47.916 A:middle
You can play around with
this if you haven't already.

