There's a "Forgot
Apple ID or password?"

00:22:29.876 --> 00:22:31.736 A:middle
So if the user has
forgotten their ID,

00:22:32.036 --> 00:22:34.536 A:middle
we'll manage the whole
flow of helping them

00:22:34.536 --> 00:22:36.866 A:middle
to remember their
password or reset it.

00:22:37.326 --> 00:22:41.206 A:middle
And finally, if the user
is brand new to, you know,

00:22:41.206 --> 00:22:43.766 A:middle
the Apple ecosystem, they
don't have an Apple ID at all,

00:22:44.096 --> 00:22:46.666 A:middle
