00:23:15.196 --> 00:23:20.816 A:middle
Public database usage is the
same for iOS, OS X and web.

00:23:20.816 --> 00:23:22.816 A:middle
There's no difference,
so a request made

00:23:22.816 --> 00:23:24.496 A:middle
on the web is the
same as a request made

00:23:24.646 --> 00:23:26.386 A:middle
on your phone or on your Mac.

